reviewText: Dont know who ordered this product.

Buffie the Body, the big booty phenomenon creates her own video which is somewhat about a day in the life of what she does. Well the parts about the magazine shoot is pretty good, some of the audio and video needs work, especially the scenes of her hosting a party. The booty clap scene was the bomb!!! But overall, she does have it going on. I just hope the next video she creates will be much better and more professional polished than this one.
